Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • worldofzuul.Command

  • public class Command
extends java.lang.Object
    This class handles user-given commands. Contains methods to determine: - If the user command is two words - If the user command is an 'unknown' -> "?" entry - Getter methods for commandWord and secondWord
